#

Maple Glazed Salmon with Cauliflower Mash

$25
480 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreePaleo

Tags:

PopularHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A sweet and savory dish featuring succulent salmon glazed with a rich maple syrup, served on a bed of creamy cauliflower mash.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Maple syrup: 3 tbsp
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Cauliflower: 1 medium head
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • Chives: for garnish
